	url = {https://translate.google.com/?sl=zh-CN&tl=en&text=Key%20Changes%0A%0Aprocess_lapis.py%3A18-176%20now%20drives%20the%20full%20pipeline%3A%20loads%20weathon%2FLAPIS_Captioning%2C%20streams%20each%20image%20through%20Ollama%E2%80%99s%20qwen25vl3b_q8%2C%20attaches%20all%20metadata%2C%20generates%20a%20one-sentence%20prompt%2C%20evaluates%20the%20image%20with%20hpsv2.score%2C%20maintains%20twin%20tqdm%20progress%20bars%2C%20and%20saves%20the%20augmented%20split(s)%20with%20the%20new%20prompt%20and%20score%20columns.%0AEnvironment%20setup%20done%20for%20you%3A%20upgraded%20Pillow%2C%20installed%20hpsv2x%2C%20the%20Ollama%20Python%20client%2C%20and%20the%20Ollama%20runtime%3B%20created%20the%20qwen25vl3b_q8%20model%20from%20Theta-Lev%2FQwen2.5-VL-3B-Instruct-Q8_0-GGUF%20because%20the%20lighter%20Q4%20quantization%20returned%20corrupt%20text.%20CUDA%20is%20detected%20(NVIDIA%20GH200%20480GB)%2C%20so%20both%20Ollama%20and%20HPSv2%20will%20accelerate%20automatically.%0ADry%20run%20executed%20with%20python%20process_lapis.py%20--limit%202%20--splits%20train%20--output-dir%20processed_lapis_sample%3B%20the%20sample%20result%20is%20saved%20locally%20and%20published%20at%20weathon%2FLAPIS_Captioning_qwen25vl_sample%2C%20confirming%20the%20workflow%20end%20to%20end.%0AProgress%20bars%3A%20first%20(prompt%20generation)%2C%20second%20(HPSv2%20scoring)%3B%20both%20advance%20per-row%20so%20you%20get%20live%20status%20across%20long%20runs.%0A%0ANext%20Steps%0A%0ALaunch%20the%20full%20job%20(e.g.%20python%20process_lapis.py%20--output-dir%20processed_lapis_full)%20without%20--limit%3B%20expect%20several%20seconds%20per%20image%20because%20generative%20inference%20is%20the%20bottleneck.%0APush%20the%20completed%20dataset%20to%20your%20preferred%20Hugging%20Face%20repo%20once%20the%20run%20finishes%2C%20using%20datasets.load_from_disk(...).push_to_hub(...).%0AMonitor%20GPU%2FVRAM%20usage%20(nvidia-smi)%20during%20long%20runs%E2%80%94Qwen%20VL%20Q8%20is%20~3.3%E2%80%AFGB%20plus%20H